name: ⭕️ MLNDR Founders Collection: 005/Mila
description: Meet Mila. The MLNDR’s furry little friend 😻. Mila is an advanced, genetically modified kitten from Pawbert Industries®, running firmware v7.32 and she is up to date with all her digital bioprint® shots. She was enhanced by Aaron with a 750% cognitive boost which gives her the ability to learn names and speak basic English. She has learned +3000 words so far and counting! Set in a dystopian future where natural resources are scarce and pollution is a global problem, the MLNDR Family Series will portray how I see our future as a species if our hunger for non-renewable natural resources continues to grow at the current pace. The Founders collection will be comprised of 6 characters who will play as leading actors in my MLNDR Family series. Holders of this token participate for a chance to win one of 10 NFTs from my props collection.
